{"id":280748,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-70名上访维权人士庆祝元宵节被警方带走做/","date":"2013-02-25T04:30:45Z","modified":"2013-02-25T04:30:45Z","title":"维权网 | 70名上访维权人士庆祝元宵节被警方带走做笔录（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员华新、疾风报道）本网信息员于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>点半左右接到黑龙江访民徐兆杰电话得知：</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日下午</span><span>，来自全国各地的约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span></span><span>名访民在北京大兴区康庄路口舒漫迪歌舞厅庆祝元宵节，大家欢聚一堂，有说有笑在唱歌。不想大兴区公安局清源路巡逻大队却闻讯前来，没有理由就强行将他们带去清源路巡逻大队，现正在清源路巡逻大队审讯，登记每个访民的名字。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据徐兆杰访民最后一次来电说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span>多访民中有来吉林的曹月春，来自湖北的田兰，来自湖北黄玲，来自辽宁的贾凤芹，来自的天津张兰英等等，还有许多不知名的访民。她刚拍了两张照片就拍不到了，警察将访民们一个个分开来问话，分别做笔录。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当本网信息员还想与徐兆杰多了解情况时，她的手机被告之已关机。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">44</span><span>分，常年在北京上访、有家难归，无法与亲人团聚共度元宵佳节的陕西访民吕动力，北京访民李焕君，上海访民吴玉芬、吴爱英、朱萍萍、程玉兰，辽宁访民赵广君，还有王素娥以及部分蒙冤警察等人，准备在北京市大兴区康庄路口舒曼迪歌厅庆祝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年的元宵节，没想到竟然在歌厅门口被</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>多名警察包围，然后全部抓走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>吕动力</span><span> </span><span>电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13021151218</span></div>\n<div><span>徐兆杰手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18645311020</span></div>\n<div><span>黄玲手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13261919066</span></div>\n<div><span>贾凤芹手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">130211282854</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>图：约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span>名访民在舒漫迪歌舞厅庆祝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QH_S0qVYqXc/USoe0TR98cI/AAAAAAAAd24/2yWXZ1FO7Lo/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QH_S0qVYqXc/USoe0TR98cI/AAAAAAAAd24/2yWXZ1FO7Lo/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-9iirq4ADi5Y/USoe6DOJLfI/AAAAAAAAd3A/F0Oofc6aidM/s1600/9.jpeg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-9iirq4ADi5Y/USoe6DOJLfI/AAAAAAAAd3A/F0Oofc6aidM/s320/9.jpeg\" width=\"250\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}